CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 18, 1961, pg. A14 reads: "Kappa Karnival Guests got a real bang out of the party held at the Anchorage, last Friday night...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Men and women gathered around banquet table with bottles, including man Howard Thomas wearing Kappa Alpha Psi fez, standing next to wife Harriet Thomas, in the Anchorage for Kappa Alpha Psi's Kappa Karnival
